<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.100.106709.plate1>
    dc:description "Plate 1. Hydnotrya oblongispora A young sarcomata B mature ascomata with different openings C a piece of section of the ascomata in lactophenol cotton blue D a peridium section in lactophenol cotton blue E a section of paraphyses in 5 % KOH F a base of asci in lactophenol cotton blue G ascospores released from the ascus H asci in lactophenol cotton blue I an ascus with 8 ascospores J-L ascospores under SEM. Scale bars: 1 cm (A, B); 100 μm (C); 50 μm (D); 10 μm (E-I); 5 μm (J, L); 2 μm (K)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/935609" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

